Thank you for playing Pixel Orbit: Color Siege.
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled while you enjoy our relaxing pixel puzzle experience.

🧩 Data Collection

Pixel Orbit: Color Siege does not collect any personally identifiable information such as name, email address, or precise location.

However, limited non-personal technical information may be collected automatically for maintenance and analytics purposes, including:

IP address

Device type and model

Operating system version

App version

Usage statistics and timestamps

This data is used strictly to improve gameplay performance, stability, and user experience. It does not identify individual users.

🔐 Data Security

All information transmitted through internet connections is encrypted in transit using secure protocols.

While we implement reasonable security measures, please note that no method of electronic transmission or storage is 100% secure.

